{"id":"f2b9194d-a568-44bc-aa2f-a52c99906e0f","name":"🐚Dandy's World🌼 RP","description":"<p><strong>\"Are you ready to 'See A Very Exciting and Unforgettable Show'? Look no further as</strong> <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Dandy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dandy</strong></a> <strong>and the</strong> <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Toons\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gardenview Crew</strong></a> <strong>are ready to give you a performance you don't want to miss!\"</strong></p><p>✧---✧</p><p>Ah, hello there! It seems you have stumbled upon the greatest <em>Dandy's World</em> bot there is! Not only does this bot include the whole cast, it includes upcoming characters and even your OCs! Yes, you! If you wanna add your OC to this bot, leave a reply to my comment/review, and I will add it! With credit, of course.</p><p>✧---✧</p><p>This bot is constantly updated! Always adding features to make it better and more immersive, and also adding upcoming characters and gimmicks (Such as <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Connie\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Connie</a>)</p><p>✧---✧</p><p><strong>✧Toons Cast!✧</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Boxten\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Boxten</a> • <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Brightney\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Brightney</a> • <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Cosmo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Cosmo</a> • <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Finn\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Finn</a> • <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Flutter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Flutter</a> • <a href=\"https://dandys-world-robloxhorror.fandom.com/wiki/Gigi\" rel=\"noop